                               Table "public.products"
   Column   |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |      Default      
------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+-------------------
 id         | uuid                        |           | not null | gen_random_uuid()
 nome       | character varying(255)      |           | not null | 
 categoria  | character varying(50)       |           | not null | 
 descricao  | text                        |           | not null | 
 preco      | numeric(10,2)               |           | not null | 
 estoque    | integer                     |           | not null | 0
 imagem     | text                        |           |          | 
 created_at | timestamp without time zone |           |          | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
 updated_at | timestamp without time zone |           |          | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
Indexes:
    "products_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "idx_products_categoria" btree (categoria)
Check constraints:
    "products_categoria_check" CHECK (categoria::text = ANY (ARRAY['tradicional'::character varying, 'premium'::character varying, 'especial'::character varying, 'refrigerantes'::character varying]::text[]))
    "products_estoque_check" CHECK (estoque >= 0)
    "products_preco_check" CHECK (preco > 0::numeric)
Referenced by:
    TABLE "order_items" CONSTRAINT "order_items_product_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(id)
Triggers:
    update_products_updated_at BEFORE UPDATE ON products FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at_column()

